<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Game of Life</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta content="Conway's Game of Life" name="description">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        html {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: black;
        }
        
        .main {
            height: 100dvh;
            width: min(100% - 2rem, 30rem);
            margin-inline: auto;
            padding-block: 2dvh;
            display: flex;
            gap: 5px;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        
        .board {
            background: black;
            gap: 1px;
            padding: 2px;
            margin-inline: auto;
            max-width: min(100%, 30rem);
            display: grid;
            aspect-ratio: 1/1;
            grid-template-rows: repeat({{boardSize}}, 1fr);
            grid-template-columns: repeat({{boardSize}}, 1fr);
        }
        
        .tile {
            transition: background 0.4s ease;
        }
    </style>
    <script type="module"
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/starfederation/datastar@v1.0.0-beta.1/bundles/datastar.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<main id="morph" class="main">
    <h1>Conway's Game of Life</h1>
    <p>Built with ‚ù§Ô∏è using
        <a href="https://kotlinlang.org/">Kotlin</a>,
        <a href="https://http4k.org/">http4k</a>
        and
        <a href="https://data-star.dev/">Datastar</a> üöÄ
    </p>
    <p>Original source code can be found
        <a href="https://github.com/http4k/examples/tree/master/http4k-core/datastar/game-of-life/src/main/kotlin">here</a>
    </p>
    <div id="game-board-container">
        <div class="board" id="game-board" data-on-load="@get('/game-board')">
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
</body>
</html>
